      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-accepting-a" mid="9" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Yes, of course.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="8"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>Have a moment for my tale?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-accepting-a" image="QW_23.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-accepting-b" mid="11" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="10"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain${action:Talk}<BR>During the <FONT color=#a82424>Calderock Struggle</FONT>, a great battle was fought at the <FONT color=#a82424>Road of No Return</FONT>. We held on strong, with key strategic positions secured and the support of our people.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-accepting-b" image="QW_23.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-accepting-c" mid="13" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>What happened thereafter?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="12"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>But war is never kind. Many good folks lost their lives there. It was a tragic loss to many families.<BR>After the battle, people called the place, <FONT color=#a82424>Road of No Return</FONT>, because nobody was able to return alive.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-accepting-c" image="QW_23.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-accepting-d" mid="15" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="14"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>Although that happened a long time back, Calderock still caries its battle scars. Look, I've one here too. (A wide jagged scar runs along his left arm)<BR>Losing my master at Forest of Death was bad enough and just a few days after, I've lost my one and only friend. (Sobs)</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-accepting-d" image="QW_23.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-accepting-e" mid="70" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="69"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>I went back to the <FONT color=#a82424>Road of No Return</FONT> for the death anniversary of my friend. When I got there, I found something that wasn't there before.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-accepting-e" image="QP_Manufactory.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-accepting-f" mid="17" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="16"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>I found a <FONT color=#a82424>Poison Machine</FONT> at a dead end of Road of No Return.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-accepting-f" image="QP_Manufactory.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-accepting-g" mid="19" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="18"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain${action:Talk}<BR>I couldn't stay away from town for long so I had no choice but to return quickly. Since then, that <FONT color=#a82424>Poison Machine</FONT> has been always on my mind. <BR>Could you check out the place and find out who put such a machine there?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-accepting-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-accepting-acceptted" mid="21" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html><FONT color=#086171>Accept Quest</FONT></html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="20"><![CDATA[<html>$Invisible Body I$</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1" image="QP_Manufactory.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="22"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>When you get to the end of <FONT color=#a82424>Road of No Return</FONT>, you will see a machine. I'm afraid the monsters may be up to no good again. Please find out if this is so.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n255_invisible_thief-1" image="QW_23.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="24"><![CDATA[<html>$???$<BR>Seems like there's something here.<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Go to Road of No Return)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n026_trader_may-1" image="QW_23.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="25"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant May$<BR>Did you notice something about Jermain? He has been brooding about something ever since he returned from Road of No Return. I wonder what happened to him.<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Go to Road of No Return)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n269_invisible_thef_sq333_334-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n269_invisible_thef_sq333_334-1-a" mid="27" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Surprised) What are you talking about?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="26"><![CDATA[<html>$Invisible Thief$<BR>Hey there, explorer. <BR>Just so you know, you've being a great annoyance right now.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n269_invisible_thef_sq333_334-1-a" image="QP_Manufactory.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n269_invisible_thef_sq333_334-1-b" mid="29" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>It does not belong you anyway. You stole it from the monsters...</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="28"><![CDATA[<html>$Invisible Thief$<BR>You BROKE my <FONT color=#a82424>almost-precious poison macine</FONT>. I was going to make a fortune with this.<BR>It would have been worth quite a lot given its size. You should take responsibility!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n269_invisible_thef_sq333_334-1-b" image="QP_Manufactory.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n269_invisible_thef_sq333_334-1-c" mid="31" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>But still, stealing is a bad thing to do.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="30"><![CDATA[<html>$Invisible Thief$<BR>Ok! I stole it!<BR>I needed it to make enough gold to help me return my body to its original state!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n269_invisible_thef_sq333_334-1-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n269_invisible_thef_sq333_334-1-d" mid="33" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="32"><![CDATA[<html>$Invisible Thief$<BR>Alright, ok. Relax. It wasn't like I'm stealing because I like to steal.<BR>But I admit It was fun at first after I became invisible. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n269_invisible_thef_sq333_334-1-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n269_invisible_thef_sq333_334-1-e" mid="35" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="34"><![CDATA[<html>$Invisible Thief$<BR>Soon, I realized that , even if I was invisible, I couldn't become like Phantom Thief Shupin, or a sorcerer. Therefore, in all honesty, I stole it because I wanted to become my old self again. Do you understand?<BR>I mean, can you understand how lonely it is to be invisible?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n269_invisible_thef_sq333_334-1-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n269_invisible_thef_sq333_334-1-f" mid="37" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>In that case, let's find a cure together.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="36"><![CDATA[<html>$Invisible Thief$<BR>Do you know what it took to move the machine here? I only wanted to sell it and this... this.... *Sniff sniff*... had to happen... *Sniff sniff*. I only wished to earn some money... Why me?? But you had to come along and break it and I even had to get scolded by a kid!... *Sniff sniff*.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n269_invisible_thef_sq333_334-1-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n269_invisible_thef_sq333_334-1-g" mid="39" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Maybe he's talking about... May?) First, let's return to the town and talk there.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="38"><![CDATA[<html>$Invisible Thief$<BR>You.. you'll help me?<BR>Yaaaay! You should look for the person who made the Super Detergent last time. The person who made it did wonders with it. I'm sure that person can help</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n269_invisible_thef_sq333_334-1-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n269_invisible_thef_sq333_334-1-h" mid="41" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Well then, I'll be back again. Try not to get your hopes up too much, ok?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="40"><![CDATA[<html>$Invisible Thief$<BR>No. no town for me.<BR>I have nothing there.. no home, no friends to talk to... It's just so sad</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n269_invisible_thef_sq333_334-1-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n269_invisible_thef_sq333_334-1-i" mid="89" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Okay.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="42"><![CDATA[<html>$Invisible Thief$<BR>Ok, just take it as saving someone who is destined for great achievements.<BR>You are all I've got, hero!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n269_invisible_thef_sq333_334-1-i" image="QW_24.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="90"><![CDATA[<html>$Invisible Thief$<BR>
Oh my, don't come here anymore.<BR>
I will be at <FONT color=#a82424>Death Basin</FONT> so find me there.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n269_invisible_thef_sq333_334-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="43"><![CDATA[<html>$Invisible Thief$<BR>When I'm visible again, the first thing I will do is to buy the best clothes I can find. <BR>You'll be the first to see my handsome face if you can find me the cure.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n026_trader_may-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="44"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant May$<BR><FONT color=#a82424>Cleric Jermain</FONT> told me that he encountered something strange at Road of No Return. Is it true?<BR>I'm so~ curious.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-2-a" mid="83" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(You explain the situation)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="45"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>You're back!<BR>So, did you find out what those monsters were up to with that machine?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-2-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-2-b" mid="50" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>He says that he is staying away from the town.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="49"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>A thief...? <BR>Hmm...<BR>If you can bring him to me, I think I will be able to help him with my spiritual powers.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-2-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-2-c" mid="52" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>It is quite incredible...</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="51"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>Really? Spirituality and beliefs cannot be forced upon someone. It is really up to him. But being invisible? That's incredible.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-2-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-2-d" mid="85" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html><FONT color=#086171>(Receive Reward)</FONT></html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="84"><![CDATA[<html>$Quest Reward$</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-2-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-2-!next" mid="88" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Let me ask May about it first.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="87"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>How are you going to find the cure?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
